### Priority Scoring API Test Examples
### Run these with REST Client extension in VS Code

### 1. Login (get JWT token first)
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8787/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Calculate Priority Score - Single Issue
POST http://localhost:8787/api/ai/priority-score
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "issue": {
    "location": "Mumbai",
    "urgency_level": "high",
    "affected_people_estimate": 500,
    "needs": ["medical", "shelter"],
    "summary": "Major flood with casualties"
  }
}

### 3. Calculate Priority Score - Medium Priority
POST http://localhost:8787/api/ai/priority-score
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "issue": {
    "location": "Delhi",
    "urgency_level": "medium",
    "affected_people_estimate": 200,
    "needs": ["food", "water"],
    "summary": "Food shortage in slum area"
  }
}

### 4. Rank Multiple Issues - Top 5
POST http://localhost:8787/api/ai/priority-rank
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "issues": [
    {
      "id": "1",
      "location": "Mumbai",
      "urgency_level": "high",
      "affected_people_estimate": 500,
      "needs": ["medical", "shelter"],
      "summary": "Major flood with casualties"
    },
    {
      "id": "2",
      "location": "Delhi",
      "urgency_level": "medium",
      "affected_people_estimate": 200,
      "needs": ["food", "water"],
      "summary": "Food shortage in slum area"
    },
    {
      "id": "3",
      "location": "Chennai",
      "urgency_level": "high",
      "affected_people_estimate": 50,
      "needs": ["medical"],
      "summary": "Medical emergency - small group"
    },
    {
      "id": "4",
      "location": "Kolkata",
      "urgency_level": "low",
      "affected_people_estimate": 1000,
      "needs": ["education"],
      "summary": "School renovation needed"
    },
    {
      "id": "5",
      "location": "Pune",
      "urgency_level": "high",
      "affected_people_estimate": 3000,
      "needs": ["shelter", "food", "water"],
      "summary": "Earthquake displacement"
    }
  ],
  "topN": 3,
  "includeBreakdown": true
}

### 5. Rank Issues - Without Breakdown
POST http://localhost:8787/api/ai/priority-rank
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "issues": [
    {
      "id": "1",
      "location": "Hyderabad",
      "urgency_level": "medium",
      "affected_people_estimate": 150,
      "needs": ["clothing", "food"]
    },
    {
      "id": "2",
      "location": "Bangalore",
      "urgency_level": "low",
      "affected_people_estimate": 25,
      "needs": ["education"]
    }
  ],
  "includeBreakdown": false
}

### 6. Error Case - Missing Issue
POST http://localhost:8787/api/ai/priority-score
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "issue": null
}

### 7. Error Case - Empty Issues Array
POST http://localhost:8787/api/ai/priority-rank
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "issues": []
}
